original_result.completion_text:
Completion: `Hello \u001b[32mTHIS IS GREEN\u001b[0m`

This completion uses Unicode escape sequences (`\u001b`) instead of literal escape characters (`\27`), which might be more compatible with various environments when handling ANSI escape codes represented as strings. Remember, the exact representation can depend on whether the environment supports interpreting these escape codes.
